Class XMLSampleDataImporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.sampledata.XMLSampleDataImporter

  • public class XMLSampleDataImporter
extends Object
    Utility for loading sample data from xml files. Works the same as the Admin import tool (see ImportDataInfo.importFromInputStream), with minor differences surrounding error handling (conflicts are ignored, in this case)
